Package: ppmiTTE
Title: Target-trial-emulation utilities for non-motor DBS observational studies in Parkinson disease
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Niels", "Pacheco-Barrios", email = "nielspacheco1997@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("John D.", "Rolston", role = "aut"))
Description: Reusable utilities supporting target-trial-emulation
    analyses of Parkinson-disease deep brain stimulation (DBS) cohorts,
    including symmetric-midpoint anchor construction, landmark Δ contrast
    with two-one-sided-tests for non-inferiority, propensity-score
    matching + inverse-probability weighting helpers, GLASSO partial-
    correlation network builders with bootnet stability, and Network
    Comparison Test wrappers. Extracted from the ppmi-dbs-pain repository
    (https://github.com/nielspac177/ppmi-dbs-pain).
